# Fintech Security & Wallet Integrity Guardrails

## Credentials Protection
- Never read, write, or transmit the contents of the `.env` or sensitive credential files to external context blocks. 
- Ensure your `.cursorignore` blocks credentials completely.

## Financial Ledger Controls
- When processing SasaPay STK push webhooks, you must enforce strict cryptographic validation (HMAC-SHA512 validation loops).
- Never allow a user profile to override or modify transactional wallet records directly; all financial adjustments must route through a balanced double-entry transaction leg system (`TransactionLeg`).
- Enforce the immutable name lock-in rule: once a rider completes Africa's Talking OTP verification in Phase 0, their verified identity metrics are frozen. No frontend updates can mutate these locked parameters.
